haha, mindslicer, that's a great quote. do you mind if I use it in my signature?<br>
<br>
1. The main character is usually emotionally unstable, and lying about his past.<br>
<br>
2. Girls are comfortable fighting in extremely tight/revealing clothing.<br>
<br>
3. It's possible to fight with a weapon twice as large as yourself.<br>
<br>
4. It's cool to shout one-liners, even if nobody's there to hear them.<br>
<br>
5. Large glowing objects can save your current &quot;status.&quot;<br>
<br>
6. If you commit any major crimes, hide out for a while, and eventually the cops will stop looking for you.<br>
<br>
7. If your squadron is deserted on an alien planet/establishment, you're the only one who's going to make it out alive.<br>
<br>
8. Townspeople are very generous, and will let you into their homes if you so please.<br>
<br>
9. You can grind off of virtually anything on your rollerblades.<br>
<br>
10. There are usually people who want you dead for no reason whatsoever. <p><hr color=#000000><div align="center"><i>"I think I'd get the 12x12 [tablet] and use it as a coffee table. It'd be a great conversation piece."</i><br>-SpikesCafe, <i>K.T.F.O.T.</i></i></br>
